Package com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct

Class Proteome<T extends Protein>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct.Proteome<T>
  • public class Proteome<T extends Protein>
extends java.lang.Object
    The Proteome class holds an ObservableList of Protein objects, as well as experimental parameters such as concentration and temperature labels. It can call the ImportWizard class to populate the Proteome. In addition, this class performs functions over the collection of Protein objects, including calling Normalisation classes to normalise the Proteome.
